social_posts.post_text:
Benfica and benfiquistas, you will always have a special place in my heart. ❤️ Thank you for allowing me to be a part of this amazing club and allowing me the opportunity to grow and learn as a player and person. Though I am sad to leave, I am very excited for what the future holds for me. Thank you so much for supporting me throughout my time here 🫶🏼 Swag Goalie out 🫡

Benfica e benfiquistas, terão sempre um lugar especial no meu coração. ❤️ Obrigada por me permitir fazer parte deste clube incrível e me permitir a oportunidade de crescer e aprender como jogador e pessoa. Embora esteja triste por partir, estou muito animado com o que o futuro me reserva. Muito obrigada por me apoiar durante todo o meu tempo aqui 🫶🏼 Swag Goalie out 🫡
Portugal, thank you for the summer 🫶🏼☀️

Very happy to announce I have signed with a West Ham United @westhamwomen, a club that has always welcomed me. For now I will be loaned to Djurgårdens IF @dif_fotboll in Sweden. I am very grateful for this amazing opportunity and challenge, that I couldn’t be more ready to take on!

So excited to announce that I will be joining Djurgårdens IF @dif_fotboll on loan from West Ham United @westhamwomen. This is an amazing club in a high level league, and I am looking forward to the rest of this season and the next!
Happy to have had my debut with @dif_fotboll
